commitResults.messageTitle: Create Filter-by-tag Command, Fix Ui-BusinessSize / List Bug
commitResults.messageBody:
The filter command filters all contacts by the tag specified as arguments.
In cases where multiple tags are specified, filter will list only the contacts
which match all the tags.

Fix Ui-Business bug which was causing Contact cards to not show.
Moving forward, lets make sure all @FMXL references exist in the fxml file itself before adding
the fields. Doing so will make sure no Ui bugs occur.

commitResults.messageBody:
